If it is HashMultimap type then do some other operation. How can i check and pass the object to another function.
Please using this api: Iterator.next.

If the element is an instance of the HashMultimap class, you can perform a different operation by calling the processHashMultimap() function and passing the hashMultimap as a parameter.
